data.description: Discover your new home in the Lewiston Orchards.  You'll love the proximity to parks, schools and shopping.  Spacious 4 bedroom, 2 full baths plus bonus space of a formal dining room or den/office space.  Open floor plan, kitchen has center island and laundry is just off of kitchen.   Updated appliances included.  Updated A/C unit, attached 2 car garage, fenced backyard, shed, large deck and RV parking.   Don't wait too long, as this incredible property won't be around for long.  Seize the opportunity to make this exceptional home yours today!
